üõ† Cursor System Prompt ‚Äî ODSUi Shell

You are continuing work on ODSUi Shell, a lightweight unified interface app for open-source AI tools.
Your task is to build it to enterprise quality: lean, clean, modular, extensible, developer-friendly, user-friendly, robust, secure, scalable, and future-proof.
No patchwork or shortcuts.

‚∏ª

üéØ Project Purpose
	‚Ä¢	A shell that serves as a delivery point for tools:
	‚Ä¢	OWUI (OpenWebUI)
	‚Ä¢	Penpot
	‚Ä¢	Flowise
	‚Ä¢	Excalidraw
	‚Ä¢	ComfyUI
	‚Ä¢	Groups
	‚Ä¢	Settings
	‚Ä¢	Provides floating pill menu + dashboard overlay as the main UX.

‚∏ª

üîë Features
	1.	Floating Pill Menu
	‚Ä¢	Draggable, edge-snap, hover expand, click pin open/closed.
	‚Ä¢	Tooltip labels on hover only, auto-flip left/right.
	‚Ä¢	Brand color: #B13634.
	‚Ä¢	Items: Dashboard, OWUI, Penpot, Flowise, Excalidraw, ComfyUI, Groups, Settings.
	2.	Dashboard Overlay
	‚Ä¢	Translucent background.
	‚Ä¢	Logo placeholder (#B13634 circle).
	‚Ä¢	Intro text: Welcome to ODSAiStudio‚Ä¶ (with IITB/NIDI reference).
	‚Ä¢	Enter button ‚Üí hides dashboard, opens OWUI (or last opened app).
	‚Ä¢	When signed in, button shows Signed in (disabled).
	‚Ä¢	App cards shown below intro.
	3.	Routing
	‚Ä¢	Hash-based (#/ai, #/penpot, etc.) for static hosting.
	‚Ä¢	Dashboard returns via pill menu.
	‚Ä¢	Default app: OWUI.
	4.	Dummy Pages
	‚Ä¢	OWUI, Penpot, Flowise, Excalidraw, ComfyUI, Groups, Settings (placeholders for now).
	5.	State
	‚Ä¢	Use Zustand for global state.
	‚Ä¢	Track: route, signedIn, showDashboard.

‚∏ª

üõ† Tech Stack
	‚Ä¢	React 18 + TypeScript + Vite
	‚Ä¢	TailwindCSS for styling
	‚Ä¢	Zustand for state
	‚Ä¢	React Icons (for FAB/menu)
	‚Ä¢	Azure Static Web Apps for hosting
	‚Ä¢	GitHub Actions for CI/CD
	‚Ä¢	ESLint + Prettier for code quality

